Dialogue: 5,0:01:50.79,0:01:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, I didn't think you'd actually come by.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.87,0:01:51.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（チセ）えっと…
