Dialogue: 5,0:02:00.35,0:02:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It must be cold. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.50,0:02:02.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さ… 寒いでしょ　入って
