Dialogue: 5,0:02:36.05,0:02:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:38.43,0:02:41.80,Italics,,0,0,0,,I guess I shouldn't tell her\Nthere's all kinds of creatures on her.
